#. <section class="sutta" id="sn10.6"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn10.6:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn10.6:0.2"
msgid "1. Indakavagga"
msgstr "1. With Indaka"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn10.6:0.3"
msgid "6. Piyaṅkarasutta"
msgstr "6. With Piyaṅkara"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn10.6:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā anuruddho sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa "
"ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time Venerable Sāriputta was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

msgctxt "sn10.6:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā anuruddho rattiyā paccūsasamayaṃ paccuṭṭhāya "
"dhammapadāni bhāsati."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time Venerable Anuruddha rose at the crack of dawn and recited "
"passages of the teaching."

msgctxt "sn10.6:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho piyaṅkaramātā yakkhinī puttakaṃ evaṃ tosesi:"
msgstr ""
"Then the native spirit Piyaṅkara’s Mother soothed her little child, saying:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.452"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. <a class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc826"></a>
msgctxt "sn10.6:2.1"
msgid "“Mā saddaṃ kari piyaṅkara,"
msgstr "“Don’t make a sound, Piyaṅkara!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn10.6:2.2"
msgid "Bhikkhu dhammapadāni bhāsati;"
msgstr "A mendicant recites passages of the teaching."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn10.6:2.3"
msgid "Api ca dhammapadaṃ vijāniya,"
msgstr "When we understand a passage,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn10.6:2.4"
msgid "Paṭipajjema hitāya no siyā."
msgstr "we can practice for our welfare."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
#. <a class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc827"></a>
msgctxt "sn10.6:3.1"
msgid "Pāṇesu ca saṃyamāmase,"
msgstr "Let us keep from harming living creatures,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn10.6:3.2"
msgid "Sampajānamusā na bhaṇāmase;"
msgstr "and speak no lying words."

#. <br>
#. VAR: susīlyamattano → susīlamattano (bj, mr)
msgctxt "sn10.6:3.3"
msgid "Sikkhema susīlyamattano,"
msgstr "We should train ourselves well in ethics,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn10.6:3.4"
msgid "Api muccema pisācayoniyā”ti."
msgstr "and hopefully we’ll be freed from the goblin realm.”"
